The paper deals with domain adaptation, which is a common problem in machine learning, and proposes a method to align the learned representations by embedding specific Domain Alignment Layers in any given network. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), or Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
